[Unit]
Description=Update Checker Service
After=network-online.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=pi
WorkingDirectory=/home/pi/projects/BACnetTest
ExecStart=/home/pi/projects/BACnetTest/venv/bin/python -m src.update_checker
Restart=always
RestartSec=60

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

---

## **API Endpoints You'll Need:**

**1. Check for updates:**
```
POST /api/device/check-update
Body: {device_id, current_version}
Response: {update_available: bool, target_version: string}
```

**2. Report update status:**
```
POST /api/device/update-status
Body: {device_id, success: bool, version, error}
```
